public class ITunesTableUI
extends BasicTableUI

A UI delegate that renders an iTunes style table. Sorting indicators will be rendered if a TableUtils.SortDelegate is installed on the associated JTable via the TableUtils.makeSortable(javax.swing.JTable, com.explodingpixels.widgets.TableUtils.SortDelegate) method.
